dct_description_sm: Large city map plus Index Map of entire city. Small Index Map showing Townships and Wards in color. This map section is partitioned between South Atlantic city as main map and a detail of Longport in upper left hand corner. This is the upper left quadrant of a large map that has been divided into 4 digital images.
